00:00:50.987 --> 00:00:54.903
So we're going to make it 2x-3

00:00:54.903 --> 00:00:57.666
times 3x+1

00:00:57.666 --> 00:01:00.961
times 3x+1

00:01:00.961 --> 00:01:03.771
