00:01:03.771 --> 00:01:07.315
plus something else

00:01:07.315 --> 00:01:10.240
over 2x-3

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:13.096
2x-3

00:01:13.096 --> 00:01:14.872
times 3x+1.

00:01:14.872 --> 00:01:19.202
Times 3x+1.

